\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529683\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 28, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lqs1665702762288.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lqs1665702762288.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lqs1665702762288.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lqs1665702762288\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Uniface <span class=\"ph\">10.4</span>.01: Repository Changes\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__unifacerepository_changes_1942\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__p_d830e1_d831e1_d832e1\">Changes have been made to the Uniface Repository that will allow new features to be added to the Uniface IDE, such as fine-grained version control for library objects, and searching and filtering on resources.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__p_d833e1_d834e1_d835e1\">The following fields have been added to all *.DICT entities:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__li_d308e1_d309e1_d310e1\">UKEYWORDS (W256)—for future enhancements.  </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__p_d836e1_d837e1_d838e1\">The following fields have been added to *.DICT entities for sub-objects. They are already available for main development objects.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__li_d311e1_d312e1_d313e1\">UPURPOSE (C1)—for future enhancements.  </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__li_d314e1_d315e1_d316e1\">UTIMESTAMP (E)—for future enhancements.  </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__p_d839e1_d840e1_d841e1\">The following fields have been enlarged:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__li_d317e1_d318e1_d319e1\">UDESCR (W256)—description of the object; increased from 64 to 256 Unicode characters.\n <p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__li_d320e1_d321e1_d322e1\">UALT_NAME (W128)—descriptive name for the object, which\n            can include formatting characters; increased from 64 to 128 Unicode characters. <p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cvv1665702762433.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cvv1665702762433.html\" title=\"This property defines a descriptive name for a palette. This name is displayed in the Resource Browser instead of the object name. It can contain up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Alternative Name</a>. </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"lqs1665702762288__note_w1325ab1b5c15_w1326ab1b5_w1327ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> Do not run Uniface <span class=\"ph\">10.4</span> against an earlier Repository, and do not use\n      earlier meta model definitions in Uniface 10.3.</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nyx1665702764465.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface 10: Repository Changes</a><p>To support the new Uniface IDE, changes have been made to the Uniface Repository. This means that it is not possible to run the Uniface IDE against a Uniface 9 Repository or even a Uniface 10.3 Repository, so you must migrate your application sources to the new Repository. The changes have no impact on runtime behavior.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gag1665702764590.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface 10: Repository Changes per Entity</a><p>This topic lists the new, changed, and deleted fields for each Repository entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529683\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529683\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface 10.4.01: Repository Changes Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 28, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface 10.4 .01: Repository Changes Changes have been made to the Uniface Repository that will allow new features to be added to the Uniface IDE, such as fine-grained version control for library objects, and searching and filtering on resources. The following fields have been added to all *.DICT entities: UKEYWORDS (W256)—for future enhancements. The following fields have been added to *.DICT entities for sub-objects. They are already available for main development objects. UPURPOSE (C1)—for future enhancements. UTIMESTAMP (E)—for future enhancements. The following fields have been enlarged: UDESCR (W256)—description of the object; increased from 64 to 256 Unicode characters. For more information, see Description . UALT_NAME (W128)—descriptive name for the object, which can include formatting characters; increased from 64 to 128 Unicode characters. For more information, see Alternative Name . CAUTION: Do not run Uniface 10.4 against an earlier Repository, and do not use earlier meta model definitions in Uniface 10.3. Related Links Uniface 10: Repository Changes To support the new Uniface IDE, changes have been made to the Uniface Repository. This means that it is not possible to run the Uniface IDE against a Uniface 9 Repository or even a Uniface 10.3 Repository, so you must migrate your application sources to the new Repository. The changes have no impact on runtime behavior. Uniface 10: Repository Changes per Entity This topic lists the new, changed, and deleted fields for each Repository entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}